{"about_the_game":"<strong>&quot;Isn't it tiring to go into the dungeon all the time to farm materials? So why don't we tame the monsters and raise them in our ranch?&quot;</strong> - <i>Archie &amp; Chloe Flamvell (player)</i><br><br>Graduating from the Artisan Academy, the bright minded twin decided to open up an Artisan Workshop with a farm that grows their own materials and a ranching monsters from the dungeons. Combining <strong>exploration</strong> and <strong>RPG elements</strong>, taking care of the <strong>farm and monsters</strong>, and <strong>forming bonds</strong> with the villagers, the twin aims to become the best artisan the world has ever seen.<br><br>If you love the idea of <strong>being an artisan and taming monsters in your farm</strong>, and want to be notified for the latest news, join us here<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fantasy Farm and Monster Ranching</h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2505510/extras/Farm_and_Ranch.gif?t=1728628430\" /><br><br>Cultivate unique plants to use on your recipes, take care of various monsters to produce more materials. Happy monsters will produce <strong>special materials</strong> and unhealthy monsters will escape your farm.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Explore Dungeons and Tame Monsters</h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2505510/extras/Explore_and_Tame.gif?t=1728628430\" /><br><br>The monsters inside all the different dungeons may have different behaviors, some are docile, some are aggressive, some are shy and run on sight, and there are those pesky ones who try to steal your items. With a their <strong>favorite food</strong> and a strategy to calm the monsters down, you can persuade them to join your ranch.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Craft and Raise your Artisan Rank</h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2505510/extras/Collect_and_Craft.gif?t=1728628430\" /><br><br>With all the material gathering done, it's time to practice your artisan skills. Craft tons of recipes from <strong>swords and weapons, potions and candies, clothes and toys, delicious cooking, and anything you can think of.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Experience a Carefree Fantasy Life</h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2505510/extras/Experience_Fantasy_Life.gif?t=1728628430\" /><br><br>Don't let your work as an artisan stops you from enjoying a carefree fantasy life in Clover Islands. 4 islands with different cultures and <strong>52 villagers</strong> with <strong>14 of them being romanceable</strong>, surely you won't run out of stories to experience. Tie your fate and weave new stories with your new family in Artisan Story.<br><br><br><i>This game is a work in progress!</i><br>Remember that the game is still in development and the footage is not final. Follow our socials for the latest updates of our work!","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2505510/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728628430","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2505510/page.bg.jpg?t=1728628430","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2505510/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1728628430","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2505510/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1728628430","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<h1>SUPPORT US ON KICKSTARTER</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2505510/extras/ks-steam.png?t=1728628430\" /></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>&quot;Isn't it tiring to go i